{"word":"στρατεύω","slug":"στρατεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>στρατεύω</el></b> [<el>στρατός</el> ‘army’; ‘wage war’] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> ‘serve on a military force’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> be on (military) duty <a href='B:490 3:14'>Lk 3:14</a>; <a href='B:530 9:7'>1 Cor 9:7</a>; <a href='B:620 2:4'>2 Ti 2:4</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> engage in combat <a href='B:540 10:3'>2 Cor 10:3</a>; <a href='B:610 1:18'>1 Ti 1:18</a>; <a href='B:660 4:1'>Js 4:1</a>; <a href='B:670 2:11'>1 Pt 2:11</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:στράτευμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:στρατηγός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}